<lb ed="C I" n="0035b04"/>丙□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沓</unclear>法□□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b05"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">發</unclear>西不<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">朽</unclear>□誠□乎<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">品</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">仲</unclear>
