<lb ed="C I" n="0035b08"/>約賓等尸鳩。故以剋<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">挫</unclear>之
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b09"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">妣</unclear>言施於安子俠溫飽是
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b10"/>陶豈非天性。陶又武□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b11"/>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">刺</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">刑</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">部</unclear>終復襲爵者。
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b12"/>當<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">非</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">義</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歆</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear>吾封<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">非</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淹</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b13"/>兄弟不得獨自跨擁。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0035b14"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">逮</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">世</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">輝</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">則</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">不</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">及</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孫</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">故</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">銘</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>。</p>
